# Phase 12: Profile Refactor & Polish

## Goal Description
Enhance the Profile Page to fetch real data from Supabase, ensuring accurate user stats, videos, and community posts. Also add a global search feature.

## Proposed Changes

### Profile Page Refactor
#### [MODIFY] [app/profile/[username]/page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/profile/[username]/page.tsx)
- Fetch profile data by username from `profiles` table.
- Fetch videos by `profile.id` from `videos` table.
- Correctly calculate `isOwner` using [useAuth](file:///C:/GoLive/components/AuthProvider.tsx#22-23).
- Pass `profile.id` to [CommunityTab](file:///C:/GoLive/components/CommunityTab.tsx#23-200).

#### [MODIFY] [components/CommunityTab.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/CommunityTab.tsx)
- Add `channelId` prop.
- Filter posts by `channelId`.
- Only show "Create Post" input if `isOwner`.

### Global Search
#### [NEW] [components/SearchBar.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/SearchBar.tsx)
- Simple input that redirects to `/search?q=...`.

#### [NEW] [app/search/page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/search/page.tsx)
- Results page fetching videos matching title/description.

## Verification
- **Profile**: Visit `/profile/username`, verify real avatar/videos show.
- **Owner**: Visit own profile, verify "Edit" buttons appear. Visit others, verify they don't.
- **Search**: Search for "game", see relevant videos.
